ygData.messageBody:
Well, I finally created a character on the Brell
Server by the name of Listeria. She is a cleric of
Errolossi(sp?) Marr. Hope to see you all soon.

Elizabeth (Silarus (Errolossi Marr), Olexia (Fennin
Ro)and Listeria (Brell)
